Enumeration Type Documentation

anonymous enum

Enumerator:
STATE_START_OCG  initiate OCG
STATE_GET_OPT  get options of OCG command
STATE_DETECT_FILE  detect the configuration file in folder USER_XML_FOLDER
STATE_INI_EMU  initiate an emulation after finding a configuration file
STATE_PARSE_FILENAME  parse the filename into user_name and file_date
STATE_CREATE_DIR  create directory for current emulation
STATE_PARSE_XML  parse the configuration file
STATE_SAVE_XML  save the configuration file to the created directory
STATE_CALL_EMU  call the emulator
STATE_GENERATE_REPORT  generate some information of OCG
STATE_END  lead to an end of the OCG process
